---
description: AGDD governance rules for this repo
alwaysApply: true
---
Read `/AGENTS.md` and `/governance/AGENTS.md` first — they are authoritative. The `governance`
repo is the Source of Truth (ADRs, specs, invariants 1–25, contracts, policies).

- One submodule per change; never span two in a commit.
- Dependency direction: webfrontend → bff → backend → governance (governance depends on nothing).
- Spec-first + TDD. New decision → Proposed ADR in governance and stop. API change → governance PR first.
- Full loop: /governance/docs/process/agdd.md. Definition of Done: /governance/docs/process/definition-of-done.md.
